column2: b'Tennis no Ouji-sama: Another Story - Kako to Mirai no Message Specials'

b"These specials feature the Oshitari cousins in a Manzai (\xe6\xbc\xab\xe6\x89\x8d) setup [a style of stand-up comedy in Japan, which usually involves two performers\xe2\x80\x94a straight man (tsukkomi) and a funny man (boke)].

Story 1 involves Oshitari Yuuhi who is tired of being the tsukkomi and wants to try his hand at being a boke but with disastrous results.

Story 2 is about Oshitari Kenya in the role of a boke whose jokes didn't get through to the audience in a joint Namiwa-Seishun Talentshow."
